{"id":14574,"date":"2013-06-05T11:29:15","date_gmt":"2013-06-05T07:29:15","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/www.dailyhadithonline.com\/?p=14574"},"modified":"2019-06-17T14:21:52","modified_gmt":"2019-06-17T10:21:52","slug":"love-allah-no-fear-sadness","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/06\/05\/love-allah-no-fear-sadness\/","title":{"rendered":"Hadith on Love: They love for Allah, have no fear or sadness"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Umar ibn al-Khattab reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201c<b>Verily, among the servants of Allah are people who are neither prophets nor martyrs, yet\u00a0the prophets and\u00a0martyrs will admire them on the Day of Resurrection due to their position before Allah Almighty<\/b>.\u201d They said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, tell us who they are.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201c<b>They are people who love each other with the spirit of Allah, despite having no shared family relations or wealth. By Allah, there will be light on their faces and they will be upon light. They will not fear when people are afraid, and they will not be sad when people are grieved.<\/b>\u201d Then, the Prophet recited the verse, \u201c<strong>Certainly,\u00a0<\/strong><b>the allies of Allah will have no fear, nor will they grieve.<\/b>\u201d (10:62)<\/p>\n<p>Source: <span class=\"il\">Sunan<\/span>\u00a0Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 3527<\/p>\n<p>Grade: <b><i>Sahih<\/i><\/b> (authentic) according to Al-Albani<\/p>\n<p align=\"right\">\u0639\u0646 \u0639\u0645\u0631 \u0628\u0646 \u0627\u0644\u062e\u0637\u0627\u0628 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0628\u0650\u064a\u064f\u0651 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e <b>\u0625\u0650\u0646\u064e\u0651 \u0645\u0650\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u06